      <title>欧洲的季节性气体差异使交易者保持警惕</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-06/europe-s-volatile-seasonal-gas-spread-keeps-traders-alert</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲夏季和冬季天然气合同之间的蔓延中的急剧波动使它成为贸易最热门的工具之一，因为官员辩论如何在下一个暖气季节填补燃料储备。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-06/europe-s-volatile-seasonal-gas-spread-keeps-traders-alert</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 06 Mar 2025 08:11:04 GMT</pubDate>
